## Per-Channel Group Size Support for LUT Quantization

Adds support for configurable per-channel group sizes in LUT quantization.
Default per_channel value is 8 if not specified.

**Format:** `bits` or `bits,per_channel`
**Example:** `--lut2 4,4` (4 bits with group size 4) or `--lut2 4` (4 bits with default group size 8)

